name: Starmine
description: Mine asteroids, get NFTs, earn $SMT and BNB, become a space tycoon! In this out-of-this-world adventure, you'll navigate through the vastness of space, strategically managing your resources to maximize your crypto yield. Upgrade your mining rigs with BNB-powered technology, hire bot experts to automate your operations, and compete in intergalactic leaderboards for bragging rights and even more BNB rewards!
